OL,3,C'We're broken, never to be fixed': Two
OL,4,Cmums fundraise for heart screening
OL,6,FDonna, from in Dalton-in-Furness in
OL,7,FCumbria, lost her daughter Vicky
OL,8,FParker, 30, to a sudden cardiac attack
OL,9,Fon the 17th of August 2023. The fit
OL,10,Fand healthy mother-of-two had no prior
OL,11,Fsymptoms.
OL,13,F"She travelled to Oxford with her
OL,14,Fpartner and the girls, went on the
OL,15,Ftrain, basically got to the house they
OL,16,Fwere stopping in with family members
OL,17,Fand I don't think she had even been
OL,18,Fhere an hour and she was sat in an arm
OL,19,Fchair and she had a cardiac arrest,"
OL,20,FDonna said.
