OL,3,C'We're broken, never to be fixed': Two
OL,4,Cmums fundraise for heart screening
OL,6,FTwo weeks later, Lesley Mease's son
OL,7,FWilson Shepherd, who was very athletic
OL,8,Fand ran multiple triathlons, died from
OL,9,Fa Sudden arrhythmic death syndrome
OL,10,F(SADs) aged 25 on the 31st August 2023.
OL,12,FLesley said she had seen Wilson the
OL,13,Fday before he died and "he was
OL,14,Fabsolutely fine".
OL,16,F"Me and my daughter were walking my
OL,17,Fgranddaughter the next morning and
OL,18,FWilson's girlfriend said 'has either
OL,19,Fof us seen or heard from Wilson'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
