OL,3,C'We're broken, never to be fixed': Two
OL,4,Cmums fundraise for heart screening
OL,6,F"I think reality is starting to set in
OL,7,Ffor both of us now very much and it is
OL,8,Fnow becoming very, very real, that
OL,9,Fthis is it forever", Donna added.
OL,11,FAccording to the charity Cardiac Risk
OL,12,Fin the Young (CRY), 12 young people in
OL,13,Fthe UK lose their lives to sudden
OL,14,Fcardiac death every week and in 80 per
OL,15,Fcent of those cases, there are no
OL,16,Fprior symptoms.
OL,18,FIn the wake of their loss, Donna and
OL,19,FLesley turned to each other for
OL,20,Fstrength ` and a purpose.
