OL,3,C'We're broken, never to be fixed': Two
OL,4,Cmums fundraise for heart screening
OL,6,FTogether, they're raising money for
OL,7,FCRY to fund lifesaving cardiac
OL,8,Fscreening days for people under the
OL,9,Fage of 35 which could help identify
OL,10,Fabnormalities and save lives.
OL,12,FOne screening day through CRY costs
OL,13,F#6,800 and Donna and Lesley are
OL,14,Fdetermined to fund as many as possible
OL,15,Fto spare other families from the pain
OL,16,Fthey continue to endure.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
