OL,3,C'We're broken, never to be fixed': Two
OL,4,Cmums fundraise for heart screening
OL,6,FDonna said: "There is nothing we can
OL,7,Fdo to save ours now, but what we can
OL,8,Fdo is try and stop it happening again.
OL,9,FIf (the heart screening) just picked
OL,10,Fup one, and saved them and saved their
OL,11,Ffamilies from going through this
OL,12,Fabsolute nightmare that we've now got
OL,13,Fto live for the rest of our lives."
OL,15,FLesley added: "Whether our children
OL,16,Fcould have been saved, we don't know
OL,17,Fbut we wouldn't want it to happen to
OL,18,Fanybody else."
